::Bloodystrike::

Bloodystrike nods, turning around and flying toward the cave. The sound of 
KitKat's voice, telling Gotron not to forward anything to Zardus, reaching 
him as he lands. KitKat must have forgotten that Bloodystrike was under 
Zardus' command, he thought, ordering Alliance members not to forward info 
was kinda useless.

He walks into the cave, his internal computer already formulating a report of 
the battle.
